# Free Stamp PNG Generator

Create transparent stamp PNG images online for free.

This tool allows you to easily generate electronic stamps or extract stamp areas from images and convert them into transparent PNG files.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Create stamp PNG images online
- Remove background from stamp images
- Export high-quality transparent PNG
- No login required
- Fast and easy to use

---

## 🧰 Use Cases

- Create electronic stamps for documents
- Add stamp to PDF files
- Generate company seal or personal stamp
- Convert scanned stamp images to transparent PNG

---

